<P>
To carry out this strategy is of great importance for the
country's prosperity and the Chinese nation's revival, he stressed.
</P>
<P>
Jiang noted the great significance for China of fostering a
large numbers of professionals and opening up more research
fields, and cited this as "a long-term strategy for the country's
future prospects and future status in the world".
</P>
<P>
He asked local governments at all levels to give strategic
priority to the developing education. China's development will
have great expectations when the education section is well
developed and the country achieves its goals of fostering
professionals and developing science and technology, he said.
