penalties in favour of Rapid and the failure to send off a Bacau
defender who fouled an attacker.
</P>
<P>
The outcome, combined with Steaua Bucharest's 1-0 defeat of
lowly Farul Constanta, propelled Steaua into two-point lead atop
the standings with only two matches left and virtually assured
them of the title. 
