Kha Phieu, Prime Minister Phan Van Khai, and Councillors of the
CPV Central Committee Do Muoi, Le Duc Anh and Vo Van Kiet attended
the funeral.
</P>
<P>
Linh, a former general secretary of the CPV, died on April 27
at the age of 82.
</P>
