sticking to socialism. He enforced the leadership of the CPV,
while respecting people's rights as the masters of the nation,
Phieu added.
</P>
<P>
"Linh was an outstanding student of Chairman Ho Chi Minh and
also a prestigious leader of the Vietnamese party, people and
army," Phieu said.
</P>
<P>
After the memorial meeting, Vietnamese leaders and tens of
thousands of Ho Chi Minh city residents escorted Linh's coffin to
the city cemetery.
</P>
