industrial base in northeast China, invested 3.45 billion yuan in
expressway construction in 1997.
</P>
<P>
The figure was 300 million yuan more than the total investments
in expressway construction between 1991 and 1995, according to local
sources.
</P>
<P>
The total mileage of the expressways under construction now in
the province stands at 471 kilometers.
</P>
