the Sino-Portuguese Joint Liaison Group at a plenary session in
Lisbon. An earlier report on the Macao Daily News said the new
foundation is expected to start operation in the coming summer.
</P>
<P>
The foundation will be supported mainly by the STDM, which
monopolizes Macao's casinos. STDM will have to hand in a certain
proportion of its gross income to the foundation, according to a
contract signed by the Macao Government and the STDM last year.
