vitality to the establishment of Sino-US constructive strategic
partnership geared towards the 21st century," said the foreign
minister.
</P>
<P>
A series of high level visits and consultation have taken place
recently between the two countries, and new progress has been
witnessed in the bilateral cooperation in some important fields
such as culture, education and public health, Tang noted, adding
that all these will help to create sound atmosphere to ensure
Clinton's China visit a success.
</P>
