forward the development of the bilateral ties and Clinton's China
visit will definitely accelerate the advancement of the US-China
relations.
</P>
<P>
The U.S. side hopes that through Clinton's visit, the American
people would enhance the understanding of China, she noted.
</P>
<P>
The United States holds that the advancement of the US-China
ties would help to maintain peace and stability in the world, and
contribute to the establishment of the constructive strategic
partnership oriented towards the 21st century between the two
countries.
