<HEADLINE> Canadian Funds Help Laid-Off Chinese Women </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LANZHOU, April 29 (Xinhua) -- This capital of northwest China's
Gansu Province is to hold a number of professional training
courses for local women who have been laid off by state-owned
companies, according to local officials.
</P>
<P>
